        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lasia1919/" class="name">作词人的错</a>

            <span class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>

        <span content="2009-09-25" class="main-meta">2009-09-25 20:52:33</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/2404764/">《夕阳天使》的前世今生</a></h2>

                <div id="review_2404764_short" class="review-short" data-rid="2404764">
                    <div class="short-content">

